                                <Image Source="Assets/target-logo-Recovered.png" Margin="0,20,0,0"/>
                                <TextBlock Text=" "/>
                                <TextBlock Text="This is an application all about giving information about top coaching institutes and Exams of Engineering. It also provides information about top colleges of India and their is also a section for experts choice. This application helps in targeting the suitable institution exclusively for you. Tips and Tricks are their to kill anxiety and nervousness of students. This application includes all the ingredients to make you a successful engineer.
" TextWrapping="Wrap" TextAlignment="Justify"/>
