                                    </StackPanel>
                                </StackPanel>
                            </GridViewItem>


                        </StackPanel>
                    </Grid>

                    <Grid>
                        <GridViewItem x:ConnectionId='5' Width="400" Margin="50,0,0,0" VerticalAlignment="Top" Name="grdHistory"                             >
                            <StackPanel>
                                <TextBlock Text="Tips and Tricks" FontSize="20"/>
                                <TextBlock Text="When Students are up to giving any entrance exam for Admission in the Colleges, Universities and many other institutes they have a lot of nervousness And anxiety in there mindsets about the Respective Exams such queries in the mindset of students are like this that will that question paper be tough or simple or will i make it for that exams merit which I m going to appear just now." TextWrapping="Wrap" TextAlignment="Justify" Margin="0,20,0,0"/>
                                <TextBlock Text=" "/>
                                <TextBlock Text="These Kind of Queries in the students results in nervousness and anxiety in there minds which effect the students during there exams time for preparation and also at the time of exam. Question paper for entrance exams are set on a fixed pattern which results in a balance of complete query type mind testing questions including some Numerical problems." TextWrapping="Wrap" TextAlignment="Justify"/>
                                <TextBlock Text=" "/>
                                <TextBlock Text="Students have a major problems with cracking of numerical that how formula can be applicable on that particular question to solve it instantly. some of them are very shortened whereas some of them are very much lengthy, complicated as well as very much time consuming an prepared student can solve that query even on its TIPS." TextWrapping="Wrap" TextAlignment="Justify"/>

